Saṅkhyāvāra
Suddha
91.
2794Nahetuyā catuvīsati, naārammaṇe catuvīsati, naadhipatiyā catuvīsati, naanantare catuvīsati, nasamanantare catuvīsati, nasahajāte vīsati, naaññamaññe vīsati, nanissaye vīsati, naupanissaye tevīsati, napurejāte tevīsati, napacchājāte sattarasa, naāsevane catuvīsati, nakamme catuvīsati, navipāke catuvīsati, naāhāre vīsati, naindriye bāvīsati, najhāne catuvīsati, namagge catuvīsati, nasampayutte vīsati, navippayutte cuddasa, noatthiyā nava, nonatthiyā catuvīsati, novigate catuvīsati, noavigate nava.
